INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
=========================

Please see the Readme.<yourplatform> file in the doc/ subdirectory for
quick installation instructions:

  Linux users: doc/Readme.Unix
  Windows users: doc/Readme.MinGW
  Mac OS X users: doc/Readme.MacOSX

For detailed, platform specific installation instructions please
read the InstallGuide.pdf file under the doc/ subdirectory.

If you find an error or missing information in these documents, please help us
improve them by letting us know about it.


